&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with all applicable regulations, policies, and bank procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a dual focus in supporting business banking as well as consumer banking service &amp;amp; sales opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage branch lobby traffic and ensure effective lobby management and branch coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for cash drawer operations and balancing, with a strong emphasis on daily focus for branch operational excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
