&lt;p&gt;First National Bank&lt;em&gt; of America&lt;/em&gt; is looking for an accountable &lt;strong&gt;Retail Loan Officer&lt;/strong&gt;. In this role, you will have all the benefits of a traditional Loan Officer with the added benefit of receiving leads generated by our in-house Marketing team. &amp;nbsp;As a nation-wide lender, First National provides you with the opportunity to originate loans in all 50 states using our niche, Non-QM Loan products. FNBA prides itself on providing exceptional customer service to educate &amp;amp; guide our clients through our loan process, while building long-term relationships with referral partners. &amp;nbsp;This role offers unmatched potential for growth, while working in conjunction with our in-house underwriting &amp;amp; operations teams. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;At FNBA, you will be able to use your existing industry knowledge and build on that with extensive, comprehensive training on our portfolio loan products and proprietary lending guidelines.&amp;nbsp; You will have access to a suite of niche mortgage products tailored toward the fastest growing segment in mortgage lending: Non-Qualifying Mortgages. We service all of our loans and have a unique perspective on underwriting that allows us to say &quot;yes” when other lenders say “no.&quot; &amp;nbsp;If you are motivated, hard-working, and enjoy helping people, we would like to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;
